postgres_fdw and gp2gp

The postgres_fdw module provides the foreign-data wrapper postgres_fdw, which
can be used to access data stored in external PostgreSQL servers.

gp2gp, based on postgres_fdw, provides the foreign-data wrapper which can be
used to access data from parallel segments of external Greenplum servers.

reference: https://github.com/greenplum-db/gpdb/wiki/Greenplum-to-Greenplum
